and I can't move!

00:19:31.212 --> 00:19:33.965 position:50% align:center
Oh, no! You got stuck
to my metal button.

00:19:34.049 --> 00:19:35.342 position:50% align:center
Don't move, okay?!

00:19:35.425 --> 00:19:37.594 position:50% align:center
