your entire eyelid!

00:19:37.677 --> 00:19:39.471 position:50% align:center
--Shiraishi!
--Huh?

00:19:39.554 --> 00:19:40.847 position:50% align:center
[SUGIMOTO]
Come here!

00:19:40.930 --> 00:19:42.140 position:50% align:center
[SHIRAISHI]
Something wrong?

00:19:42.223 --> 00:19:43.475 position:50% align:center
Come and piss on her face!

00:19:43.558 --> 00:19:44.476 position:50% align:center
[SHIRAISHI gasps]

00:19:44.559 --> 00:19:46.644 position:50% align:center
[ASIRPA]
Huh?! Do what on my face?!

00:19:46.728 --> 00:19:48.271 position:50% align:center
Uh, eh-- No, wait!

00:19:48.355 --> 00:19:50.648 position:50% align:center
Think you can pee? Right now?

00:19:50.732 --> 00:19:52.567 position:50% align:center
Ah! Yeah?

