00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:10.585 position:50% align:center
[SHIRAISHI]
Yah-ha-ha-ha-ha!

00:20:10.669 --> 00:20:12.712 position:50% align:center
[ASIRPA giggles]

00:20:12.796 --> 00:20:15.006 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:20:15.090 --> 00:20:20.053 position:50% align:center
[ALL laughing]

00:20:27.769 --> 00:20:29.729 position:50% align:center
That's enough, Shiraishi.

00:20:29.813 --> 00:20:32.899 position:50% align:center
Seriously. I'm okay now.

00:20:32.982 --> 00:20:36.069 position:50% align:center
Hey, Sugimoto!
Are you crying?

00:20:36.152 --> 00:20:39.489 position:50% align:center
Heh. Nah, it's just the piss.

00:20:44.285 --> 00:20:45.995 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Private Tanigaki!

00:20:46.079 --> 00:20:47.580 position:50% align:center
Who did this to you?!

00:20:49.624 --> 00:20:53.169 position:50% align:center
[TANIGAKI]
Kiro... ranke...

00:20:53.253 --> 00:20:54.754 position:50% align:center
That bastard.

00:20:55.714 --> 00:20:57.424 position:50% align:center
