00:20:57.507 --> 00:20:58.967 position:50% align:center
We can take care of him.

00:20:59.050 --> 00:21:01.428 position:50% align:center
[KOITO grunts]
Blood...

00:21:01.511 --> 00:21:05.181 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it's his.
He's hurt really bad-- 

00:21:05.265 --> 00:21:07.475 position:50% align:center
