00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:28.872 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
What's this string?

00:21:28.955 --> 00:21:30.081 position:50% align:center
[HAJIME grunts]

00:21:31.499 --> 00:21:32.709 position:50% align:center
