00:22:19.881 --> 00:22:20.799 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:22:20.882 --> 00:22:22.467 position:50% align:center
[KOITO grunts]

00:22:24.678 --> 00:22:25.929 position:50% align:center
[KIRORANKE growls]

